Global Civil Aircraft Cleaning Services Market Insights
Civil Aircraft Cleaning Services Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.1% from 2024 to 2030.


Civil Aircraft Cleaning Services Market Overview
The global Civil Aircraft Cleaning Services market is valued at approximately USD 3.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow significantly at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% from 2025 to 2030. This market is driven by the increasing demand for efficient aircraft cleaning due to heightened concerns over hygiene, passenger safety, and maintenance. As air travel continues to recover post-pandemic, the demand for high-quality cleaning services is on the rise, making it a key part of aircraft maintenance and operations globally.

